We are currently collecting data on bicycle thefts around the country in order to find out which areas are being targeted, how the thefts happen, whether the robbers are armed during the thefts and which bicycles are being targeted -- and we need your help. By taking just three minutes to fill out the survey below, you can be part of potentially the biggest and first bicycle data collection project in the country. In the process you'll be helping to gather as much information on this growing crime trend. The survey will be open until May 14. READ MORE: